                  <td colspan="2" valign="top" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" class="style2"><p class="style79"><strong><em>The world churns out new digital information  equivalent to the entire collection of the U.S. Library of Congress every 15  minutes</em></strong></p></td>
                </tr>
